text:
Dana Harvey (born 5 February 1989) is a New Zealand water polo player. She is a member of the New Zealand women's national water polo team. She played at the 2009 FINA World Championship.
She was educated at Rangitoto College. She played for Arizona State University's women's water polo team and California State University, Northridge's women's water polo team.
